# DB & migrations

- Exactly one Alembic head; update `tests/test_alembic_single_head_new.py` when adding revisions.
- New models → import in `models/__init__.py` for metadata coverage.
- Never weaken FK to hide bugs; fix linkage at application layer.
- SQLite tests: use `batch_alter_table` patterns from existing migrations for FK adds.
- Migrations idempotent-safe; document breaking changes in `docs/`.

## Verify

`.venv/bin/python -m pytest tests/test_alembic_single_head_new.py -q --no-cov`
